</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>

    </dt>
    <dd>{{% md %}}The monitoring schedule for snapshot analysis. For EntityType-level config: unset / disabled = true indicates disabled by default for Features under it; otherwise by default enable snapshot analysis monitoring with monitoringInterval for Features under it.
